				<text><![CDATA[For macroscopic evaluation before and/or after formalin fixation: a check of the clinical information of the specimen (e.g. type, size, number), hospital admission number and/or pathology case number and/or donor/patient ID, name and date of birth of patient and type of tissue was checked <br><font color="#004280">should</font><br>]]></text>
